config.notice=1.Use # character as comment sign and all after words are regarded as comment ignored by analyzer.\n2.When there is an object needs parameter of quantity or metadata, it needs in form of {domain:object, quantity(, metadata)}.\n3.Use 32767 to represent all objects that are the same kind but have different metadata.\n4.Press F3 + H key to see more information of objects.
config.recipes=1.Please customize recipes in the shaped form of {domain:output, {1st_row_signs(, 2nd_row_signs, 3rd_row_signs)}, {sign1, domain:input1}(, {sign2, domain:input2}, ...)}\nor in the shapeless form of {domain:output, domain:input1, domain:input2, ...}.\n2.For example, {{minecraft:gravel, 4}, {&*, *&}, {minecraft:sand, 1, 0}, {minecraft:cobblestone}} #Composing 4x[Gravel] with 2x[Sand(Sand_0)] and 2x[Cobble Stone] in &*,*& form.\nor {{minecraft:log, 1, 1}, {minecraft:log, 1, 0}, {minecraft:dye, 1, 3}} #Compose [Spruce Wood(Log_1)] with [Oak Wood(Log_0)] and [Cocoa Beans(Dye_3)] in shapeless form.
config.fuels=1.Please customize fuels in the form of {domain:object, gametick}\n2.one second equals twenty gameticks.\n3.For example, {minecraft:diamond, 200} #[Diamond] can burn for ten seconds.
config.smeltings=1.Please customize smeltings in the form of {domain:input, domain:output, acquirable_experience}.\n2.For example, {{minecraft:dirt, 1, 1}, {minecraft:dirt, 1, 2}, 0.5} #Smelt [Coarse Dirt(Dirt_1)] to [Podzol(Dirt_2)] acquiring 0.5 experience.
config.brewings=1.Please customize brewings in the form of {domain:input_potion, domain:input_material, domain:output}.\n2.For example, {{minecraft:potion, 1, 16}, minecraft:gold_block, minecraft:experience_bottle} #Brew 3x[Awkward Potion] to 3x[Bottle of Enchanting] with [Block of Gold].
config.forgings=1.Please customize forgings in the form of {domain:output, domain:input_object, domain:input_material, required_experience}.\n2.Required experience must be greater than or equal to 1, otherwise it won't be forged.\n3.For example, {minecraft:stone_sword, minecraft:wooden_sword, {minecraft:cobblestone, 2}, 1} #Forge [Wooden Sword] to [Stone Sword] with 2x[Cobble Stone] requiring 1 experience.
